  • Overview

    Note: This property is not currently for sale or for rent on Zillow. The description and property data below may’ve been provided by a third party, the homeowner or public records.

    This is a great home with newer everything throughout! Main floor has 3 bedrooms/ 1 full bath and master bath. The kitchen is a newer Schwalbach with luxury vinyl tile flooring that flows into dining area too. Three Mitsubishi AC units on main floor are a great plus! Newer high efficiency appliances and boiler combined with triple pain windows on main floor make for a very energy efficient home. There's a new big deck overlooking a huge private back yard on a big corner lot with a shed for additional storage, sit back and enjoy all the wildlife this wooded area brings while being right in town. This home is located in the Superior Heights Subdivision located very close to elementary and middle school, new hospital and Lake Superior. Great floor plan would accommodate growing family. Willing to negotiate commission to buyers agent.
